    "description": "I talk to Alex Hormozi, Elon Musk, and Ali Abdaal every morning.\n\nNone of them know I exist.\n\nHere’s the AI hack that makes it possible\n\nMost people scroll a 300-video channel and pick 3 random ones. They get 1% of that person’s actual thinking.\n\nThis is how you get all of it.\n\n→ Install Grabbit (free Chrome extension) \n→ Open any YouTube channel \n→ One click copies every single video link \n→ Paste them all into NotebookLM \n→ AI transcribes and loads the entire channel \n→ Now interrogate their whole brain\n\nWhat’s their pricing framework? How do they think about audience? What patterns repeat across their best content?\n\nAnswers in seconds. Not hours.\n\nThis used to take weeks. Now I do it before coffee.\n\nComment NOTEBOOK and I’ll send you the exact setup\n#notebooklm #alexhormozi #aiadvice",
